{
  "stem": "4693.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he started talking with Twades, and Twades told him that if we joined him, he would arrange for us-- he would come over to Romania with us to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we started going with them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And here-- she was always asking if she can drive the car.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So she was driving the car.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In the long run, we came to Siemianowice, which already was south of Poland, not very far from the Romanian border.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "As we arrived in Siemianowice, the British ambassador was already there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she asked if she could-- she had some luggage in our car-- if she can take the car and stay with the Ambassador.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We couldn't stay in the same house, we found us some other accommodations.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I told my uncle, not to-- I said, don't trust her, not to give her a car.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And my uncle told me, said, I'm stupid.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Maybe he was right.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Anyway, so he let her take the car, but he didn't have peace.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All right, so we found ourself in Siemianowice without any possibility to go further.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We met in Siemianowice with two lawyers, Poles from Katowice.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they had a car, a little Citroen and-- no, no, no.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we got into this car with them, and we decided not to go to the Romanian border, because we didn't trust the Romanians.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But to go back, and see eventually to go to Wilno.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We came as far as Dubno-- it was all in the-- and over there, we met with Mrs.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Korfanty.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Korfanty was one of the top politicians in Poland, out of the National Party, or Christian National Party.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He died.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "This was widow of Korfanty.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And as we are standing with her, came to us a guy in civilian clothes with a major.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
